火箭。这种两级液体燃料火箭设计用于从不同地点发射。它的第一次尝试在 2021 年失败了，但火箭在次年部分成功地进行了轨道发射。该公司预计将第三次为美国太空部队发射。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/firefly-aerospace-buys-the-final-scraps-of-doomed-virgin-orbit-193049970.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/firefly-aerospace-buys-the-final-scraps-of-doomed-virgin-orbit-193049970.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 8a83b550-72f3-4075-88a9-e184a8336b46</guid><dc:creator>威尔尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Fri, 16 Jun 2023 19:30:49 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686941577</ingested><modified> 2023-06-16T18:53:01+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Industrials]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="2400" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/4a6a2000-0c75-11ee-9d7b-b30a58df9b8c" width="3600"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2400" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/4a6a2000-0c75-11ee-9d7b-b30a58df9b8c" width="3600"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[DeeCee Carter/MediaPunch/MediaPunch/IPx]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Mojave, CA - December 05 : Virgin Orbit Flight Test Airplane at the Mojave Air and Space Port In Mojave, California December 05, 2020. Credit: DeeCee Carte